OL,3,CNow we expect answers, says son of
OL,4,Csoldier killed in 1994 Chinook crash
OL,6,FThe son of a serviceman killed in the
OL,7,F1994 Mull of Kintyre Chinook crash has
OL,8,Fsaid the families of the victims
OL,9,F"expect answers" ahead of a historic
OL,10,Ffirst meeting with ministers.
OL,12,FAll 29 military and intelligence
OL,13,Fpersonnel on board RAF Chinook ZD576
OL,14,Fwere killed when the aircraft crashed
OL,15,Fin foggy weather while flying from RAF
OL,16,FAldergrove in Northern Ireland to Fort
OL,17,FGeorge near Inverness on June 2, 1994.
