OL,6,F"Together with the original 110, they
OL,7,Fexpose how essential evidence was
OL,8,Fconcealed from previous inquiries and
OL,9,Fdemonstrate that the MoD has never
OL,10,Fprovided full transparency into the
OL,11,Fcircumstances that led to the deaths
OL,12,Fof 25 senior intelligence experts and
OL,13,Ffour Special Forces crew.
OL,15,F"The suggestion that no new facts will
OL,16,Fbe uncovered is a deliberate
OL,17,Fmisrepresentation to cover up past
OL,18,Fwrongdoing."
