OL,3,CNow we expect answers, says son of
OL,4,Csoldier killed in 1994 Chinook crash
OL,6,FMany of the 335 questions are based on
OL,7,Fleaked MoD technical files, internal
OL,8,Fmemos and assessments, with the
OL,9,FChinook Justice Campaign saying expert
OL,10,Fanalysis has shown the details of how
OL,11,Fand why the aircraft was authorised
OL,12,Fremain hidden.
OL,14,FThe questions include who authorised
OL,15,Fthe mission, why the Chinook Mark 2
OL,16,Fwas accepted "off contract without
OL,17,Fcertification" in breach of MoD rules
OL,18,Fand whether the crew or passengers
OL,19,Fwere informed of the risks.
