OL,3,CNow we expect answers, says son of
OL,4,Csoldier killed in 1994 Chinook crash
OL,6,FAndy Tobias, who was just eight years
OL,7,Fold when his father Lieutenant Colonel
OL,8,FJohn Tobias was killed in the crash,
OL,9,Fsaid the 335 questions are "certainly
OL,10,Fnot definitive".
OL,12,F"They are not all we need answered and
OL,13,Fthe files that are closed for 100
OL,14,Fyears are only some of the papers we
OL,15,Fwant released," he said.
OL,17,F"What this long list makes clear,
OL,18,Fhowever, is that it is simply
OL,19,Funtenable for ministers to say there
OL,20,Fis nothing new to learn.
