OL,3,CNow we expect answers, says son of
OL,4,Csoldier killed in 1994 Chinook crash
OL,6,F"We want full transparency, full
OL,7,Fcandour and to finally start getting
OL,8,Fto the full truth.
OL,10,F"We expect nothing less from our
OL,11,Fmeeting with ministers tomorrow."
OL,13,FHe added: "We have already built up an
OL,14,Funsavoury treasure trove of MoD
OL,15,Fdocuments, test pilot warnings and
OL,16,Fevidence withheld from earlier
OL,17,Finvestigations which prove my father
OL,18,Fand 28 others were put on an aircraft
OL,19,Fthe MoD knew to be unairworthy.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUsD@aO]uD@KOU
