OL,3,CNow we expect answers, says son of
OL,4,Csoldier killed in 1994 Chinook crash
OL,6,F"This is not my opinion. These are
OL,7,Ffacts the Ministry of Defence either
OL,8,Fignored, buried or refused to
OL,9,Fdisclose. We have been forced to fight
OL,10,Ffor the truth for 31 years.
OL,12,F"Now we expect answers."
OL,14,FNorthern Ireland Alliance MP Sorcha
OL,15,FEastwood, who will join the families
OL,16,Fat Tuesday's meeting, said: "If the
OL,17,Fpromise of candour is real, it starts
OL,18,Fhere.
