OL,6,F"Ministers cannot keep repeating the
OL,7,Fsame lines while refusing to answer
OL,8,Fthe families' questions.
OL,10,F"A judge-led inquiry and full access
OL,11,Fto sealed files is the only way to
OL,12,Fhonour those who died and the families
OL,13,Fwho have fought for them."
OL,15,FAn MOD spokesperson said: "The Mull of
OL,16,FKintyre crash was a tragic accident
OL,17,Fand our thoughts and sympathies remain
OL,18,Fwith the families, friends and
OL,19,Fcolleagues of all those who died.
